    "description": "圣约 是一款动作冒险游戏，带有RPG和Metroidvania元素，设定在Tessara的幻想世界中。<br>在你的兄弟阿尔瓦被背叛后，疯狂降临到了这个王国。扮演不朽的高等人类国王，你必须为王国的生存铺设一条道路。<br>在穿越古老文明的土地的疯狂旅程中，面对疯狂独裁者的疯狂追随者，与血神的崇拜者和即将到来的危险作斗争，你必须夺回你失去的权力和更多的东西来对抗你的兄弟阿尔瓦。<br>你会成为王国的守护者，作为秩序的选择吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/56ab9bc0c9e765c4f445cc9356b07e0b.webp?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/a6c125c3ebe5c94adf06e72f14d26bd9.poster.avif?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=413 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/a6c125c3ebe5c94adf06e72f14d26bd9.webm?t=1699438869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在第一人称摄影机中体验一种新的剑法，并有创新的连击。解锁多样化的魔法咒语，以困住、麻痹和烧毁你的敌人。使用你的弓来打击敌人的弱点。了解这一切，亲眼看看《Testament》的战斗有多么多才多艺和深入人心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/2f0a778c05cf3c196abeec69be9f844f.webp?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/0e042213bc6a06c739a8e0fb8152e873.poster.avif?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=413 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/0e042213bc6a06c739a8e0fb8152e873.webm?t=1699438869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>解决机械谜题并测试你的平台技能。通过克服这些考验，获得权力并了解世界的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/8285b56ce63e18ce95f4613d93fef6ca.webp?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/347ac2f77d862deec57e9a25e7ea20b7.poster.avif?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=413 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/347ac2f77d862deec57e9a25e7ea20b7.webm?t=1699438869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>世界上充满了黑暗的眼睛。阻挡者的眼睛阻挡了你的道路，水蛭的眼睛拥有其他生物，赋予他们无敌的能力，而黑夜使者则导致黑暗的降临，使你的一切变得更加困难。使用你的光之弓来摧毁这些黑暗之眼。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/73a2694683ad1b4533a67c97393109ed.webp?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/a966fe22f3a4f6f03da12daa985087ea.poster.avif?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=413 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/a966fe22f3a4f6f03da12daa985087ea.webm?t=1699438869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>使用游戏内转盘中的消耗品，看看这些魔法物品对你的游戏风格的影响。它们不是一些buff和被动的数字，使用它们来看看它们的效果有多酷和不同。不要吝惜它们，你可以在你的转盘中制作这些物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176430/extras/a38f158e06c0e44f9de267f9ce93294c.webp?t=1699438869\" width=620 height=55 /></span><br><br>成为两个高级人类兄弟Aran和Arva的故事的一部分。一个人失去了一切，但他坚持自己的信念，为自己的王国而战，而另一个人则处于吞噬他所抛弃的王国的边缘。谁能获胜将决定世界的命运。",
